Subject: drm/i915/display/icl: Disable transcoder port sync as part of
 crtc_disable() sequence
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 51528afe7c5ed6fcd6ed4cfb046b74659d21738f
Patch-mainline: v5.5-rc1
